    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planet V is a monster taming game. What makes this one different? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can catch wild monsters out of and in battle. If you can see it, just throw a Capture Cube at it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/1d6b8990e73c55f684d165f8d6084b81.avif?t=1730749341\" width=668 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy and Sell Monsters. Woo Capitalism!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/07ac397618a5849389a133df54716e4d.avif?t=1730749341\" width=530 height=412 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use items to clear environmental hazards. I'm sure you'll use this responsibly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/b1d458eb9e6d653a1f799d67c4147a5a.avif?t=1730749341\" width=530 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow affection with Monsters by discovering and appealing to each individual Monsters likes/dislikes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/076acc7ea5d17c3620024434cccddf01.avif?t=1730749341\" width=216 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain a Monster's trust to use some Monster techniques outside of battle. Thankfully not all of them breathe fire..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/a5998d9f5d1ad6b543b5f6d989bb1ad3.avif?t=1730749341\" width=310 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Edit your moves and team quickly. See your progress towards unlocking new moves. Having multiple of the same move is not a good idea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/e0120d19cd109a9cb260c1d689d97967.avif?t=1730749341\" width=800 height=670 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deeper combat featuring Stamina management, Blocking and Dodging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies will remember which techniques were ineffective against your specific Monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/7893134f5f23195e3ca872e9f82722eb.avif?t=1730749341\" width=328 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confused? Tooltips can give you more information</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/5e7a15b5f1188e255ef19535bcfa34e3.avif?t=1730749341\" width=424 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How the same area looks on different save files</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/b942287625f8af8475f8a884323a2d0f.avif?t=1730749341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras_big/b942287625f8af8475f8a884323a2d0f.avif?t=1730749341 width=800 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day/Night cycle. What's going on there?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146260/extras/8cf5af09cea7f512c8e0021f271a56c7.avif?t=1730749341\" width=800 height=478 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters can change form during battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go back and forth between your monster's forms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more to come, stay tuned!</p>",
